1) Create directory for a new project
mkdir ~/projects/inception

2) Create virtual environment for the project
python3 -m venv .

3) Some other common installations (optional):

# for a postgresql database
pipenv install psycopg2

# for a mysql database
pipenv install mysqlclient #python3
pipenv install MySQL-python #python2

# for use on heroku
pipenv install gunicorn dj-database-url

pipenv install django-crispy-forms
pipenv install pillow

4) Run Migration & Createsuperuser

python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser

